{"type":"message","id":"d26d7a8b","parentId":"d7553544","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:23:04.571Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 12:22:35 EDT] Exec completed (marine-c, code 0) :: ode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 122215.mutation rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 122115.mutation (100%) [sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 122215 - The CFI anal…\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 12:23 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-24 16:23 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774369384569}}
